 Financial Account Management Standard Objects

Add Flexibility to Financial Accounts in Service Processes with Standard Objects

Gain more control and flexibility when you use financial account information in the OmniScripts of prebuilt service processes, such as Address Update, Fee Reversal, Complaint Management, and Transaction Dispute Management. Model your customer’s financial account information in the service processes by using Financial Account and the related objects that are available either in the Financial Services Cloud managed package or in the Financial Account Management Standard Objects data model.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled.

Who: To use this feature, users need the Industry Service Excellence and OmniStudio Admin permission sets.

How: To use Financial Account and related standard objects in the financial account FlexCard components, from Setup, find and select Financial Account Settings, and then turn on Financial Account Management Standard Objects.
